Christelle Kwizera nurubyiruko afite imyaka 25, ni injeniyeri yubukanishi mu  [[Rwanda]] na rwiyemezamirimo.[https://www.vitalvoices.org/people/christelle-kwizera/]

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2014, Christelle yashinze '''Water''' Access [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.vitalvoices.org/people/christelle-kwizera/</ref>Kwizera ni '''CFO''' y'abayobozi bakizamuka hamwe na ba rwiyemezamirimo bo mu [[Rwanda]], urubuga rwo guhanga udushya mu rubyiruko, guhanga no kwihangira imirimo bashaka gushishikariza no gushishikariza urubyiruko,<ref>https://resolutionproject.org/fellows/christelle-kwizera/</ref> kubishakira ibisubizo bishya, ndetse no gutanga ubuvugizi ku bigo bya leta bireba. Kwizera yabaye umuyobozi mukuru ushinzwe ibikorwa bya Isaro Foundation<ref>https://www.pmi.org/future-50/2021-honorees/christelle-kwizera</ref>

== Ibihembo yatsindiye ==
christelle  yatsindiye ibihembo by’imishinga itanga imibereho itanga ibisubizo byihariye mu bijyanye no gukusanya, gukwirakwiza no kweza amazi. Uruganda rwahaye amazi abanyarwanda barenga 100.000 binyuze mumurongo wa boreho 95 na INUMA ™ micro isukuye amazi meza.[https://www.vitalvoices.org/people/christelle-kwizera/]

Umwamikazi Elizabeth wa II w’Ubwongereza, ku wa gatanu, tariki ya 30 Nyakanga 2014 yahaye rwiyemezamirimo w’amazi meza yo mu [[Rwanda]] Christelle Kwizera na Commonwealth Point of Light, <ref>https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/content/christelle-kwizera-cisco-youth-leadership-win-2020/</ref>ishimwe ryahawe abakorerabushake b’indashyikirwa, umurimo wabo ugira icyo uhindura mu baturage babo kandi inkuru ikaba ishobora gutera abandi inkunga guhanga udushya twibisubizo kubibazo byimibereho mumiryango yabo ndetse no hanze yacyo.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/queen-elizabeth-awards-rwandan-entrepreneur</ref>

